<p>Check In and Introduction<strong><br />Solar Energy</strong> – Ryan Mayfield, Renewable Associates, Solar Instructor<strong><br />Wind Energy</strong> – Kirk Slack, Oregon Community Wind</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Afternoon</span><strong><br />Transmission, Distribution and  Interconnection</strong> - Alan Fraser, EWEB                          <strong>Financial Fundamentals</strong> <strong>- </strong>Carolyn Roos, Washington State University<br /><strong>Hydropower</strong> – Kevin Crew, Black Rock Consulting</p>
<p><br />Evening - Dessert and Networking Opportunity   Speaker - Mike Hatten, Solarc</p>
</td>
