INSERT IGNORE INTO Articles VALUES (88,'Great combo of competency and ethics','<p>Hey Roger,</p>
<p>We talked earlier about some contacts with the Energy Trust equivalent over in the North East and Hudson Valley. Any names and numbers you have would be greatly appreciated. I plan on really digging into whats happening over there next spring, I don''t want to jump the gun too early before I leave. It couldn''t hurt to start talking to folk out there though.</p>
