<p><img style="margin: 5px; float: right;" alt="NRG173 classadflier thumb" src="images/stories/NRG173_classadflier_thumb.jpg" height="155" width="300" />Introducing a Leadership in Energy &amp; Environmental Design (LEED) online summer prep course that specifically focuses on concepts that a <a target="_blank" href="http://www.usgbc.org/credentials/leed-ga/overview">Green Associate</a> is expected to master. Learn how to apply the LEED rating system to real world scenarios!</p>
