================================================== -->
<h1>Icons</h1>
<h2>Font Awesome</h2>
<p>Font Awesome is a pictographic language of web-related actions which delivers over 300 icons. The Font Awesome webfont, CSS, and LESS files are licensed under CC BY 3.0 and you can find the full examples of usage at <a href="http://fortawesome.github.com/Font-Awesome" target="_blank">Font Awesome - http://fortawesome.github.com/Font-Awesome</a></p>
