INSERT IGNORE INTO Articles VALUES (227,'Water Conservation goes ONLINE too!','<p>Our <em><strong>Water Conservation Technician</strong> </em>Program is ONLINE.&nbsp; You can take it from anywhere!!!&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>
<p>The Water Conservation Technician program consists of an inspiring community of students and faculty dedicated to improving community water security and quality using ecologically sustainable practices. Through the two-year Water Conservation Technician online program, you will be prepared for the&nbsp;growing field of Water Conservation and the challenges a shortage of water will bring.&nbsp;</p>
<p>The Program trains individuals to evaluate water use patterns; develop, implement, market, and maintain conservation programs; perform public outreach; recommend water efficiency techniques; integrate alternative water sources, and perform systems analysis to solve problems.</p>
<p>As water-related issues continue to increase, more voluntary and mandatory water conservation opportunities are being created that require a technical skillset like that which is offered within this program. Employment opportunities in Water Conservation are excellent.&nbsp;Students must consider the Western United States when seeking employment as those willing to relocate will have greater employment opportunities.&nbsp;</p>','2019-05-23 22:14:45',NULL,22,1,'2019-05-23 22:14:45',1,1233);
INSERT IGNORE INTO Articles VALUES (228,'Modern Energy Management Podcast!','<p>Welcome to the Modern Energy Management podcast, a place for sustainability, energy, and facility innovators to tell their stories and share energy best practices that go beyond the meter. We believe that modern energy managers are individuals who use technology and best practices to harness the power of building data to improve resource efficiency, enhance employee well-being, increase operational efficiency, and to create a culture of sustainability at their organization. Tune in each week as we share Modern Energy Management stories from industry leaders who are blazing the trail.</p>
<p>&nbsp;<a href="https://lucidconnects.com/mem" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Exploring Hidden Costs of Manual Data</a></p>
<p>&nbsp;This link will take you to a multiple of good articles to listen to.&nbsp; Enjoy!</p>','2019-11-04 20:02:08',NULL,21,1,'2019-11-04 20:02:08',1,1012);
INSERT IGNORE INTO Articles VALUES (229,'Support Education and scholarships for students','<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;">&nbsp;As both Water and Energy programs expand the reach into different states, our students need support.&nbsp; Please consider giving to this effort to educate and conservation of our resources.&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">&nbsp;Read a bit of our history and see how much good work has already been done.&nbsp; But as climate changes, we need even more educational opportunities for people.&nbsp; Please help that effort.&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">&nbsp;Choose the Donate button on the right and follow the instructions.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>
